# AutoChat 🚀

An AI chatbot system with:
- Local LLM (llmware - bling-phi-3-gguf)
- FastAPI backend
- React frontend
- Chroma vector DB (RAG)
- Prometheus + Grafana observability
- Prefect pipeline for data ingestion

## Features
- Self-learning via feedback
- Semantic search (RAG)
- AI observability dashboard
- Pipeline-triggered updates

